      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a functional daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are solid and have been regularly serviced to ensure reliable performance on the road. However, please note that the exterior shows some visible signs of age, including minor scratches and paint fading, and the interior has some wear from normal use. It\u2019s a great option for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
