    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source of parts. The engine is currently running but shows signs of significant wear, including some smoke upon startup, and the transmission struggles with smooth shifting. The exterior has several large dents and peeling clear coat, while the interior requires a deep clean and repair of torn upholstery. It is recommended that any potential buyer brings a mechanic to assess the full extent of the work needed.",
