      "description": "This is the one you\u2019ve been waiting for! We are thrilled to offer this absolute gem that is in truly mint condition. It looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior and a pristine interior that has been meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for perfection and a vehicle that needs absolutely nothing, this stunning ride is ready for its new home!",
