      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards and preserved in showroom condition. This unit exhibits flawless aesthetic integrity and peak mechanical performance, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every detail has been meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our exacting criteria for excellence.",
